title: Flight Simulator 2020 - Quiz 22nd February 2021
description:
We have landed at quiz episode 9. 
In this quiz there are no POI's close to the airport. The airport is surrounded by mountains and a lot of water and is located on an island which is part of Spain.
The question is: which airport am I departing from?

DISCLAIMER: you cannot win anything except the honor ;-)
